<p><div class="left-margin" id="set-C"><h2>Characters</h2></div></p>

<ul>
  <li>
    <p><strong>Some main characters generate less impacts than their relatives</strong></p>

    <p>Elliot - He does not like military stuff and turn to be a musician. His intention is good, but I don’t think he make great impact to the main story… Instead, (His father) Olaf has more influence.</p>

    <p>Laura - (Her father) Arseid seems more proactive in the story…</p>

    <p>Machias - (His father) Carl Regnitz has more political power and seem improving the empire in some ways.</p>

    <p>Fie - The members of Zephyr take their actions in the main story, but it does not make sigificant impacts too.</p>
  </li>
  <li>
