    <p>They are not very relevant to the story, but get mentioned. I don’t think Alfin and Cedric are neccessary in the story, as they are not described in a way very impressive. They are like, they can be substituted by others with the same title. Olivert is fine, but I kinda treat him as a character from “Trails in the sky”. He has the same problem of not acting very impressive in cold steel.</p>
  </li>
  <li>
